         <abstract id="aspace_a5336759a3898742432a961a2cb5ef10">The papers consist of the lecture notes, examinations, syllabi and handouts documenting Ivan Phillips's undergraduate courses taken between 1952-1956, including courses in history, economics, and science. Also included are several grade school notebooks.</abstract>
